00:39:51.272 --> 00:39:56.368
and you can feel it,
the different centers

00:39:56.637 --> 00:39:58.980
on your fingertips
about yourself.

00:39:59.261 --> 00:40:03.654
So it is about yourself you will
know. About others, you know,

00:40:03.929 --> 00:40:06.028
you should just talk on
chakras. You should not say,

00:40:06.301 --> 00:40:09.203
