means he has got ego.

00:40:13.028 --> 00:40:15.984
You can say, his Nabhi's bad,
his, this thing is bad.

00:40:16.246 --> 00:40:17.914
So the language is
to change now.

00:40:18.189 --> 00:40:23.239
We have to talk in the
language of Sahaja Yoga.

00:40:23.939 --> 00:40:27.795
